NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Covenant - add the author's pledge to the
    distribution

VERSION
    version 0.1.1

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

        [Covenant]
        version = 1
        pledge_file = AUTHOR_PLEDGE

DESCRIPTION
    "Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Covenant" adds the file '*AUTHOR_PLEDGE*' to the
    distribution. The author as defined in *dist.ini* is taken as being the
    pledgee.

    The *META* file of the distribution is also modified to include a
    *x_author_pledge* stanza.

CONFIGURATION OPTIONS
  version
    Version of the pledge to use.

    Defaults to '1'.

  pledge_file
    Name of the file holding the pledge.

    Defaults to 'AUTHOR_PLEDGE'.

